WEBVTT

01:36.870 --> 01:40.960
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:43.200 --> 01:43.759
Xiaolan,

01:44.310 --> 01:45.200
did you have fun

01:45.200 --> 01:45.840
on this trip?

01:45.840 --> 01:46.509
Yes, I did.

01:46.840 --> 01:47.560
You did?

01:47.870 --> 01:48.870
Then let's go out every year

01:48.870 --> 01:49.560
from now on,

01:49.590 --> 01:50.120
okay?

01:50.280 --> 01:50.840
Okay.

01:51.590 --> 01:53.050
Then, Xiaolan, you decide

01:53.120 --> 01:54.720
where we should go next time.

01:59.570 --> 02:02.350
[Episode 13: The Piercing Sound of Brakes]

02:08.160 --> 02:08.919
You're up.

02:09.030 --> 02:10.630
Did you sleep well upstairs?

02:12.560 --> 02:13.420
Where is Cheng?

02:14.080 --> 02:15.520
Look at the time.

02:16.750 --> 02:17.750
He's gone to work.

02:18.079 --> 02:19.470
What was that word again?

02:19.470 --> 02:20.430
The "white"...

02:20.710 --> 02:21.570
White-collar.

02:22.310 --> 02:22.710
Right.

02:22.840 --> 02:23.800
Well, look—

02:24.150 --> 02:25.960
you just sit in an office all day
pushing paper,

02:25.960 --> 02:28.240
and they dress it up with a fancy name:
white-collar.

02:28.240 --> 02:28.800
Kang Wei.

02:29.560 --> 02:30.910
Don't forget what you said

02:30.910 --> 02:31.680
last night.

02:31.960 --> 02:33.150
A young idler,

02:33.190 --> 02:34.310
an old beggar.

02:34.360 --> 02:34.820
I'm off.

02:35.120 --> 02:36.180
Yeah, yeah, got it.

02:41.360 --> 02:42.890
Aren't you going to open one for me?

02:42.890 --> 02:44.940
[Zhiyuan Law Firm]

02:45.190 --> 02:45.800
I'm going out for a bit

02:45.800 --> 02:46.660
to see a client.

02:48.870 --> 02:49.800
Morning, Cheng.

02:49.910 --> 02:50.310
Morning.

02:50.310 --> 02:51.000
Had breakfast?

02:51.000 --> 02:51.470
Yeah.

02:51.590 --> 02:52.120
Alright.

02:56.590 --> 02:57.250
Zhou Cheng,

02:57.710 --> 02:58.910
if there's something you want to do,

02:58.910 --> 02:59.710
just go for it.

03:00.310 --> 03:01.170
Go fight for it.

03:01.560 --> 03:02.680
We may be young,

03:03.560 --> 03:05.020
but we're just as capable.

03:14.360 --> 03:14.820
Senior.

03:22.150 --> 03:22.800
Um...

03:24.280 --> 03:25.540
I want to take on a case.

03:28.630 --> 03:30.490
You want to take on a case already?

03:31.600 --> 03:32.280
I know

03:32.280 --> 03:34.010
I haven't been at the firm long,

03:34.120 --> 03:35.250
but I also remember,

03:35.560 --> 03:37.020
right here in this office,

03:37.430 --> 03:39.280
you said young people
should push themselves,

03:39.280 --> 03:40.079
take chances,

03:40.360 --> 03:42.820
break free from some rules
and constraints,

03:43.079 --> 03:44.240
and do what they want.

03:44.240 --> 03:45.590
So you're breaking the rules

03:45.590 --> 03:47.050
and coming to me for a case?

03:48.400 --> 03:48.800
Yes.

03:49.370 --> 03:50.560
But I've finished going through

03:50.560 --> 03:51.620
all the case files,

03:51.630 --> 03:53.430
I'm familiar with how the firm works,

03:53.430 --> 03:54.870
and I've helped a lot of other lawyers

03:54.870 --> 03:56.240
with prep work.

03:57.030 --> 03:58.000
I think I'm ready

03:58.360 --> 03:59.290
to take on a case.

04:01.840 --> 04:02.360
I could tell long ago

04:02.360 --> 04:03.840
that you couldn't hold back anymore.

04:03.840 --> 04:06.840
I was wondering how long you could
hold yourself back.

04:07.910 --> 04:09.400
Here. This one's yours.

04:11.120 --> 04:12.930
[Investigation Report
on the Radio Smuggling Case]

04:13.430 --> 04:14.090
Smuggling?

04:14.360 --> 04:14.710
Yes.

04:15.360 --> 04:16.040
You can take Shi Kai

04:16.040 --> 04:17.370
and work on it together.

04:18.870 --> 04:19.829
This batch of smuggled goods

04:19.829 --> 04:20.870
was found

04:20.870 --> 04:21.890
at a fisherman's home.

04:21.890 --> 04:22.920
But the fisherman insists

04:22.920 --> 04:24.450
they fished it out of the sea

04:24.480 --> 04:26.410
and didn't know it was contraband.

04:27.600 --> 04:29.190
But it's a large batch.

04:29.650 --> 04:31.000
Even if they didn't know it was smuggled,

04:31.000 --> 04:32.150
it's still of unknown origin.

04:32.150 --> 04:33.750
They shouldn't have kept it.

04:34.600 --> 04:35.630
Fishermen aren't educated

04:35.630 --> 04:36.890
and don't know the law.

04:36.920 --> 04:38.870
They probably just wanted to
make some money.

04:38.870 --> 04:40.080
That's not the same as smuggling.

04:40.080 --> 04:41.040
We still need to hear

04:41.040 --> 04:41.870
both sides.

04:43.750 --> 04:45.870
How much longer are you two going to
mope around?

04:45.870 --> 04:47.310
It was just one setback.

04:47.560 --> 04:48.680
One of you is a boss,

04:48.680 --> 04:49.950
and the other negotiates business deals—

04:49.950 --> 04:51.480
and look at yourselves now.

04:51.680 --> 04:52.920
I got you changed into these clothes,

04:52.920 --> 04:54.480
hoping to make you feel refreshed

04:54.480 --> 04:55.430
and start anew.

04:55.800 --> 04:56.659
Look at you two—

04:56.750 --> 04:57.240
do you even look like

04:57.240 --> 04:58.500
you want to start over?

04:59.560 --> 05:00.160
Kang Wei!

05:00.630 --> 05:01.360
Zhenzhu!

05:02.360 --> 05:04.190
Young people should be full of vitality,

05:04.190 --> 05:04.800
you know?

05:04.830 --> 05:06.430
Full of energy!

05:06.750 --> 05:07.610
Look at you two!

05:07.630 --> 05:08.070
I...

05:11.870 --> 05:12.670
What's wrong?

05:15.430 --> 05:16.870
Look at the two of you.

05:17.430 --> 05:19.070
No matter how beautiful the clothes are,

05:19.070 --> 05:20.270
they look lifeless

05:20.270 --> 05:21.510
on you.

05:21.550 --> 05:22.430
Exactly!

05:22.800 --> 05:24.830
Right now, you've got no spark!

05:25.630 --> 05:27.600
No energy, no confidence.

05:27.720 --> 05:29.050
Even the nicest clothes

05:29.560 --> 05:30.720
lose their value

05:30.720 --> 05:31.750
when worn

05:31.770 --> 05:33.010
by you!

05:35.720 --> 05:36.360
Granny Yu,

05:36.510 --> 05:38.840
you've seen the world
and have a sharp eye.

05:39.000 --> 05:40.920
Could you do us the honor

05:41.000 --> 05:42.659
of giving them some pointers?

05:46.270 --> 05:47.600
Look at you two.

05:48.070 --> 05:49.270
Are you still a girl?

05:49.680 --> 05:51.409
Look at the way you're sitting.

05:51.830 --> 05:53.190
Do girls sit like that?

05:53.390 --> 05:55.050
With your legs spread so wide?

05:55.560 --> 05:56.270
And you,

05:56.800 --> 05:58.510
a young man, should have energy.

05:58.510 --> 05:59.770
You need to look sharp!

06:00.070 --> 06:01.000
Stand up!

06:06.070 --> 06:07.000
A person,

06:07.270 --> 06:08.670
no matter the situation,

06:08.720 --> 06:10.950
should never slouch or hunch over.

06:11.430 --> 06:12.600
Chin up

06:12.870 --> 06:13.920
and chest out.

06:14.120 --> 06:15.070
Lift your head!

06:16.070 --> 06:17.270
That's more like it.

06:17.920 --> 06:19.720
You're in business now.

06:20.070 --> 06:21.190
You need to

06:21.190 --> 06:22.920
be conscious of your image at all times.

06:22.920 --> 06:23.510
Exactly.

06:24.120 --> 06:25.360
Granny Yu is right.

06:25.830 --> 06:26.870
When we're out in the world,

06:26.870 --> 06:28.720
we create our own persona.

06:29.040 --> 06:30.510
We must have a sense of conviction.

06:30.510 --> 06:32.600
-What... What persona? Sense of what?
-What are you talking about?

06:32.600 --> 06:33.260
Never mind.

06:33.430 --> 06:35.040
Just listen carefully to Granny Yu.

06:35.040 --> 06:35.640
Granny Yu,

06:35.920 --> 06:36.920
please continue.

06:37.600 --> 06:40.120
-Please give us some advice, Granny Yu!
-Please give us some advice, Granny Yu!

06:40.120 --> 06:41.159
That's better.

06:41.830 --> 06:43.070
Success

06:43.070 --> 06:43.750
is never easy.

06:43.750 --> 06:45.159
You have to consider
not only the brightness of the lamp

06:45.159 --> 06:47.120
but also its color temperature

06:47.120 --> 06:47.680
and frequency.

06:47.680 --> 06:49.190
Your child studies for long hours,

06:49.190 --> 06:50.720
so buying a good lamp

06:50.870 --> 06:51.870
can help

06:51.870 --> 06:53.040
protect your child's eyesight.

06:53.040 --> 06:53.600
Ms. Bai,

06:54.120 --> 06:54.950
it's a pleasure doing business with you!

06:54.950 --> 06:56.000
May we grow big and strong together

06:56.000 --> 06:57.040
and prosper as one!

06:57.040 --> 06:58.120
Let's get rich together.

06:58.120 --> 06:59.320
It's fine. It's fine.

06:59.480 --> 07:00.190
Take care!

07:06.620 --> 07:07.560
Look over here! Over here!

07:07.560 --> 07:08.600
Granny Yu, let's take a photo together!

07:08.600 --> 07:09.160
Come on, Granny Yu!

07:08.960 --> 07:11.120
[A Natural Healer]

07:09.160 --> 07:10.190
Just one photo! Just one!

07:10.190 --> 07:11.830
Granny Yu, just one. Come on!

07:12.120 --> 07:12.510
Two!

07:12.510 --> 07:12.920
Xiaolan.

07:12.920 --> 07:13.270
No!

07:13.270 --> 07:13.720
One!

07:15.000 --> 07:16.040
Alright, alright, alright!

07:16.040 --> 07:17.270
Hold the flowers, Granny Yu.

07:17.270 --> 07:17.720
Okay.

07:18.630 --> 07:19.000
Here!

07:19.750 --> 07:22.280
-Thank you, Granny Yu!
-Thank you, Granny Yu!

07:23.190 --> 07:24.950
"A natural healer?"

07:25.390 --> 07:26.920
I'm not a doctor.

07:27.480 --> 07:28.310
Oh, come on.

07:28.520 --> 07:29.130
Granny Yu,

07:29.160 --> 07:31.430
you're the doctor of our souls,

07:31.600 --> 07:32.800
a healer of our bearing!

07:32.800 --> 07:33.830
With your guidance,

07:33.830 --> 07:36.120
I feel like
I've been improving rapidly lately,

07:36.120 --> 07:38.800
and I'm now at
the starting line of success!

07:39.830 --> 07:40.480
The starting line!

07:40.480 --> 07:41.280
That's right!

07:42.690 --> 07:44.040
You've only just reached

07:44.040 --> 07:45.560
the starting line of success?

07:45.560 --> 07:47.920
Then you'd better start crawling your way

07:48.390 --> 07:49.159
up that road.

07:49.750 --> 07:51.010
Granny Yu, don't go just yet.

07:51.010 --> 07:52.430
We have one more big gift for you.

07:52.430 --> 07:52.950
Look!

07:55.510 --> 07:56.920
We've carefully chosen

07:56.950 --> 07:58.310
a chandelier for you.

07:58.390 --> 08:00.240
It suits your elegance perfectly.

08:00.240 --> 08:01.120
Let us install it for you!

08:01.120 --> 08:01.600
Hold on.

08:02.040 --> 08:03.430
Granny Yu has her rules—

08:03.600 --> 08:05.400
no one enters her room casually.

08:06.070 --> 08:06.830
Granny Yu,

08:06.920 --> 08:07.950
what do you think?

08:07.950 --> 08:09.560
Could you let them

08:09.600 --> 08:11.120
show their appreciation?

08:13.360 --> 08:14.240
Alright, go ahead, go ahead.

08:14.240 --> 08:15.310
-Okay!
-Got it!

08:15.310 --> 08:16.440
Here, let me take it.

08:16.630 --> 08:18.090
I'll open the door for you.

08:20.950 --> 08:22.270
But don't hang
that "A Natural Healer" banner

08:22.270 --> 08:23.240
for me.

08:23.240 --> 08:24.310
Okay. Hang it over the bed!

08:24.310 --> 08:24.970
Okay, okay!

08:31.070 --> 08:31.830
Granny Yu,

08:32.360 --> 08:33.440
there's something

08:33.440 --> 08:35.039
I'd like to discuss with you.

08:36.549 --> 08:38.080
What are you up to this time?

08:39.440 --> 08:40.150
Granny Yu,

08:40.440 --> 08:43.200
I'd like to ask you to help train

08:43.200 --> 08:44.260
Luna's employees.

08:44.870 --> 08:45.600
Don't worry.

08:45.910 --> 08:47.000
You won't be doing it for free.

08:47.000 --> 08:48.270
I'll pay you

08:48.270 --> 08:49.360
according to Luna's

08:49.360 --> 08:50.560
HR salary standards.

08:50.790 --> 08:53.670
Nowadays, there are
white-collar workers everywhere,

08:53.670 --> 08:55.390
and so many college graduates too.

08:55.390 --> 08:56.630
I'm just an old woman.

08:57.200 --> 08:58.720
I can't handle that kind of work.

08:58.720 --> 08:59.480
Granny Yu,

08:59.750 --> 09:00.240
look.

09:00.510 --> 09:02.240
You even know what "white-collar" means.

09:02.240 --> 09:03.500
You're so up-to-date,

09:03.550 --> 09:04.750
so don't be so modest.

09:05.280 --> 09:06.550
What I'm building this time

09:06.550 --> 09:09.080
is the first nationally branded store
of its kind.

09:09.080 --> 09:09.960
The staff inside

09:09.960 --> 09:11.870
must be distinguished from

09:11.870 --> 09:13.390
those in small, ordinary shops.

09:13.390 --> 09:15.270
I've thought it over,

09:15.480 --> 09:16.510
and only you, Granny Yu,

09:16.510 --> 09:17.870
can handle this job.

09:18.480 --> 09:20.410
You come from a prestigious family

09:20.790 --> 09:21.600
with

09:21.630 --> 09:22.910
stores in the city

09:23.000 --> 09:24.390
and businesses across Southeast Asia.

09:24.390 --> 09:26.030
A woman like you

09:26.200 --> 09:27.400
has seen everything.

09:27.870 --> 09:28.510
Besides,

09:28.790 --> 09:30.030
you're highly respected

09:30.030 --> 09:30.960
and naturally authoritative.

09:30.960 --> 09:32.790
Those young people

09:32.960 --> 09:35.290
will listen to you
the moment they see you.

09:36.960 --> 09:37.550
Alright.

09:38.600 --> 09:40.080
I'll train those girls

09:40.080 --> 09:41.030
of yours

09:41.120 --> 09:42.440
to be just like you—

09:42.600 --> 09:43.790
when they open their mouths,

09:43.790 --> 09:46.670
they make everyone feel like
they're in full bloom.

09:47.840 --> 09:49.040
Thank you, Granny Yu.

09:51.240 --> 09:52.270
When do you open?

09:53.000 --> 09:54.200
Everything is ready.

09:54.200 --> 09:55.840
We're just waiting for the final piece.

09:55.840 --> 09:57.170
I'm your "final piece"?

09:58.110 --> 09:58.660
Yes!

09:58.930 --> 10:00.280
[Luna]

10:00.960 --> 10:01.600
Ms. Xia,

10:02.120 --> 10:03.390
this "final piece" you want

10:03.390 --> 10:04.650
is nearly impossible!

10:04.840 --> 10:06.080
Getting performers
for the Chinese New Year Gala

10:06.080 --> 10:07.390
to wear our brand...

10:07.630 --> 10:09.160
You really do dare to dream.

10:09.750 --> 10:10.360
Mr. Chen,

10:10.720 --> 10:11.960
you've moved to Shengcheng.

10:11.960 --> 10:13.270
You've basically burned your bridges
to go all in.

10:13.270 --> 10:15.400
Surely, you have the fighting spirit.

10:15.480 --> 10:15.910
Fine.

10:16.200 --> 10:17.440
You dare to dream it,
and I dare to make it happen!

10:17.440 --> 10:18.640
Alright, let's do it!

10:18.840 --> 10:19.320
But can we

10:19.320 --> 10:21.000
replace the sign by the door first?

10:21.000 --> 10:22.030
That sign looks far too shabby.

10:22.030 --> 10:23.080
Okay, okay. Soon.

10:23.240 --> 10:24.270
The new one will be ready next week.

10:24.270 --> 10:26.270
With large gold-embossed letters!

10:33.080 --> 10:33.940
It's m-my wife.

10:33.960 --> 10:35.030
I'm stepping out to make a call.

10:35.030 --> 10:36.360
You go ahead and look around yourself.

10:36.360 --> 10:38.000
You should get a brick phone!

10:38.200 --> 10:40.200
I'll buy one once the company opens!

10:43.790 --> 10:44.440
Luna—

10:45.240 --> 10:47.640
the first domestic women's fashion brand.

10:48.120 --> 10:49.910
Built from nothing, it rose to glory,

10:49.910 --> 10:51.960
then fell into decline.

10:52.960 --> 10:53.840
And Chen Xiliang

10:53.840 --> 10:56.240
reached the peak of his life
because of Luna

10:56.390 --> 10:58.670
but also lost his life because of it.

10:59.960 --> 11:00.910
I used to be the most

11:00.910 --> 11:02.750
overlooked salesperson at Luna.

11:02.750 --> 11:03.390
Now,

11:03.720 --> 11:04.550
right here,

11:04.870 --> 11:06.910
I'm going to get everything I once desired

11:06.910 --> 11:08.550
but was too afraid to pursue.

11:15.240 --> 11:15.750
Ms. Xia.

11:18.480 --> 11:19.630
Is something wrong at home?

11:19.630 --> 11:20.600
It's nothing really.

11:20.600 --> 11:21.390
My wife...

11:21.750 --> 11:23.320
heard I was moving to Shengcheng.

11:23.320 --> 11:24.080
She's unhappy,

11:24.080 --> 11:25.510
so she's finding excuses to pick a fight.

11:25.510 --> 11:26.360
You came to Shengcheng

11:26.360 --> 11:28.390
to hide from your family, didn't you?

11:28.390 --> 11:29.480
The two of us...

11:29.500 --> 11:30.110
Well,

11:30.320 --> 11:32.200
our families arranged for us to meet.

11:32.200 --> 11:34.120
We didn't have any feelings for each other
to begin with.

11:34.120 --> 11:34.750
Later,

11:35.030 --> 11:36.750
her brother got into gambling.

11:36.750 --> 11:37.680
Then, every day,

11:37.870 --> 11:40.080
her family pressured her
to ask me for money.

11:40.080 --> 11:41.750
Anyway, let's not talk about that.

11:41.750 --> 11:43.510
Right now, I only have one thing
on my mind—

11:43.510 --> 11:45.150
building Luna into something great.

11:45.150 --> 11:45.610
Come on,

11:45.790 --> 11:47.050
let me show you around.

11:50.100 --> 11:50.690
Mr. Tang,

11:50.720 --> 11:52.240
you really didn't have to come with me.

11:52.240 --> 11:52.750
Look,

11:52.910 --> 11:54.320
t-the market is so chaotic.

11:54.320 --> 11:55.120
It's not chaotic at all.

11:55.120 --> 11:56.030
It's bustling!

11:56.240 --> 11:57.670
So lively, so vibrant!

11:58.550 --> 11:59.750
Excuse me! Excuse me!

12:00.120 --> 12:00.600
Excuse me, coming through!

12:00.600 --> 12:01.200
Watch out!

12:01.360 --> 12:02.750
Thanks, thanks! Sorry about that!

12:02.750 --> 12:03.550
Excuse me!

12:25.550 --> 12:26.550
Let me take a look?

12:27.910 --> 12:29.080
No need. It's nothing.

12:29.080 --> 12:29.680
Let me see.

12:35.630 --> 12:37.430
It's your zodiac year this year?

12:38.360 --> 12:39.150
No.

12:40.080 --> 12:40.600
Well...

12:42.320 --> 12:44.580
Let's buy you a new outfit to change into.

12:45.790 --> 12:46.270
Well...

12:46.790 --> 12:48.550
Good thing we're in a clothing market.

12:48.550 --> 12:50.950
Otherwise, I wouldn't know
how to fix this.

12:51.910 --> 12:52.440
Here.

12:52.790 --> 12:53.550
Cover it with my bag.

12:53.550 --> 12:54.210
Okay, okay.

12:55.030 --> 12:56.080
You go ahead, and I'll follow.

12:56.080 --> 12:56.480
Okay.

12:59.390 --> 12:59.840
This way.

12:59.840 --> 13:01.440
Well, this is embarrassing.

13:07.720 --> 13:08.550
I've never worn clothes

13:08.550 --> 13:09.240
quite like this before.

13:09.240 --> 13:09.910
Do I look okay?

13:09.910 --> 13:11.310
Yeah, you look very nice.

13:12.440 --> 13:13.040
Very nice.

13:13.870 --> 13:15.670
It makes you give off
a completely different vibe.

13:15.670 --> 13:17.180
Do I look like a businessman now?

13:17.180 --> 13:17.840
Maybe I should just join you

13:17.840 --> 13:19.040
and go into business.

13:21.450 --> 13:22.360
Once you put the outfit on,

13:22.360 --> 13:23.690
you look years younger.

13:24.120 --> 13:24.550
Sir,

13:24.840 --> 13:25.510
your wife

13:25.510 --> 13:27.370
has excellent taste in clothing.

13:27.480 --> 13:28.080
Very good.

13:38.600 --> 13:39.200
Careful.

13:44.200 --> 13:45.330
Thank you for today.

13:46.270 --> 13:47.600
Why are you thanking me?

13:47.840 --> 13:48.670
If anything,

13:48.750 --> 13:49.870
I should be thanking you.

13:49.870 --> 13:51.000
Otherwise, well...

13:51.440 --> 13:53.570
I would've embarrassed myself again.

13:53.750 --> 13:55.080
Let's not stand on ceremony between us—

13:55.080 --> 13:56.870
we're just helping each other out.

13:56.870 --> 13:57.930
Um, your collar...

13:59.630 --> 14:00.150
Collar.

14:03.440 --> 14:04.040
Well, I...

14:04.550 --> 14:06.720
I've never worn clothes like this before.

14:06.720 --> 14:08.110
I'll head back now.

14:08.870 --> 14:09.320
Okay.

14:10.030 --> 14:10.560
Goodbye.

14:10.670 --> 14:11.200
Goodbye.

14:15.280 --> 14:15.670
Bye-bye.

14:15.670 --> 14:16.040
Bye.

14:26.480 --> 14:27.010
Let's go.

14:30.720 --> 14:32.450
Big cities are just on another level.

14:32.450 --> 14:33.930
The styles, the fabrics,

14:33.960 --> 14:35.000
and the colors—

14:35.240 --> 14:36.150
they're so trendy

14:36.150 --> 14:37.150
and very stylish.

14:38.150 --> 14:39.240
I've written down the numbers

14:39.240 --> 14:40.320
of all those stalls.

14:40.320 --> 14:40.960
I'm here!

14:41.880 --> 14:42.630
Uncle, you're here.

14:42.630 --> 14:43.030
Yong!

14:48.080 --> 14:48.790
Have some water.

14:48.790 --> 14:49.360
Uncle.

14:51.310 --> 14:52.270
The bidding documents are ready?

14:52.270 --> 14:52.910
All set.

14:53.720 --> 14:56.180
I've brought
both the originals and copies.

14:56.860 --> 14:57.770
[Yuanhui Decoration Bidding Documents]

14:59.360 --> 14:59.910
Fen.

15:00.270 --> 15:01.030
You're dressed so nicely.

15:01.030 --> 15:02.160
Where have you been?

15:02.670 --> 15:03.550
Really?

15:04.120 --> 15:06.670
I went to... do some market research.

15:07.720 --> 15:09.240
The format looks fine.

15:09.600 --> 15:10.320
Whether Yuanhui

15:10.320 --> 15:12.240
can make a name for itself in Shengcheng

15:12.240 --> 15:13.370
depends on this bid.

15:13.600 --> 15:15.860
I'll go over it carefully again tonight.

15:22.250 --> 15:23.630
Didn't Uncle say we'd go together?

15:23.630 --> 15:24.770
Why aren't they here yet?

15:24.770 --> 15:26.200
Chengzi said he'd come by himself,

15:26.200 --> 15:26.910
but early this morning,

15:26.910 --> 15:28.570
he got called to meet a client.

15:41.390 --> 15:42.080
Kang Wei?

15:54.870 --> 15:55.530
Don't move!

15:55.960 --> 15:56.620
Don't move!

16:03.120 --> 16:03.650
Kang Wei.

16:04.120 --> 16:05.840
Quick, take my car
and drive Xiaolan there.

16:05.840 --> 16:06.170
Okay.

16:06.250 --> 16:07.360
I'll take this guy to the police station.

16:07.360 --> 16:08.360
Behave yourself!

16:08.550 --> 16:08.960
Uncle,

16:08.960 --> 16:09.810
are you sure you can handle this alone?

16:09.810 --> 16:11.510
Handling this punk? No problem.

16:11.510 --> 16:12.170
Let go of me.

16:12.390 --> 16:13.000
Xiaolan!

16:13.200 --> 16:13.910
Behave!

16:25.390 --> 16:25.790
Hello.

16:26.000 --> 16:26.880
-I'm here to submit the bidding documents.
-Hello.

16:26.880 --> 16:27.720
Submitting a bid, right?

16:27.720 --> 16:28.030
Yes.

16:28.120 --> 16:28.910
Just put it over there.

16:28.910 --> 16:30.240
Come on, register here.

16:34.450 --> 16:35.170
[Shengcheng Yuanhui Decoration Co., Ltd.;]

16:35.170 --> 16:35.890
[Shengcheng Guesthouse Renovation Project]
[Bid Document]

16:35.920 --> 16:37.440
[Shengcheng Guesthouse; Bidding Office]

16:38.270 --> 16:38.960
Xiaolan,

16:39.120 --> 16:39.920
that was fast.

16:40.960 --> 16:42.320
Just submitting the bid.
What more did you expect?

16:42.320 --> 16:43.610
Going in and sitting for a while for tea?

16:43.610 --> 16:45.150
I didn't think it would be that simple.

16:45.150 --> 16:45.900
After all, this bid

16:45.900 --> 16:47.320
determines Yuanhui's future development.

16:47.320 --> 16:49.270
I thought it would be
more of a grand occasion.

16:49.270 --> 16:51.150
Many life-changing events

16:51.390 --> 16:53.510
happen without you even realizing it.

16:53.510 --> 16:54.040
Let's go.

17:02.080 --> 17:02.720
Xiaolan,

17:03.150 --> 17:04.240
why did Ke Yixiong's man

17:04.240 --> 17:05.960
try to snatch our bidding documents?

17:05.960 --> 17:07.069
Liu Tianquan is the one behind this.

17:07.069 --> 17:08.970
Ke Yixiong's man just did it for money.

17:08.970 --> 17:10.440
Liu Tianquan approached Uncle before,

17:10.440 --> 17:11.770
wanting to rig the bid with him.

17:11.770 --> 17:13.790
He offered money for us to throw the bid.

17:13.790 --> 17:15.480
No way Uncle Yong would agree to that.

17:15.480 --> 17:16.640
Just throwing them out
without roughing them up

17:16.640 --> 17:18.109
would have been letting them off easy.

17:18.109 --> 17:19.310
Uncle indeed didn't let them off easy—

17:19.310 --> 17:20.839
he drove them out directly.

17:23.510 --> 17:25.109
I told you to let her have the bid,
and you went behind my back to rig it?

17:25.109 --> 17:25.680
Do you even know

17:25.680 --> 17:26.750
that I'm your young master?

17:26.750 --> 17:27.750
You darn bastard!

17:28.069 --> 17:28.750
Drive faster!

17:28.750 --> 17:29.110
Yes.

17:29.270 --> 17:30.920
Xia Xiaolan is submitting the bid today.

17:30.920 --> 17:32.000
I need to go explain everything to her.

17:32.000 --> 17:33.400
It's fine, Young Master.

17:33.580 --> 17:35.840
You don't have to get so angry, actually.

17:43.510 --> 17:44.030
A car!

17:45.160 --> 17:46.020
A car is coming!

17:47.750 --> 17:48.400
Watch out!

18:48.160 --> 18:49.090
Young Master...

18:50.510 --> 18:51.440
Are you alright?

19:27.720 --> 19:28.380
Kang Wei...

19:30.160 --> 19:30.690
Kang Wei?

19:31.030 --> 19:31.590
Kang Wei!

19:33.960 --> 19:35.400
Kang Wei! Kang Wei!

19:40.260 --> 19:41.460
Xia Xiaolan's car...

19:42.160 --> 19:43.490
It's Xia Xiaolan's car!

19:49.830 --> 19:50.510
Help!

19:50.720 --> 19:51.520
Please help!

19:51.720 --> 19:52.720
-Xia Xiaolan!
-Ms. Xia!

19:52.720 --> 19:54.120
Are you alright, Ms. Xia?

19:59.070 --> 20:00.520
Kang Wei! Kang Wei!

20:00.640 --> 20:01.030
Let's go!

20:01.030 --> 20:01.760
Xia Xiaolan.

20:01.790 --> 20:02.440
Get out of the car.

20:02.440 --> 20:03.200
Get out! It's dangerous!

20:03.200 --> 20:03.880
Let go of me!

20:03.880 --> 20:05.000
Get out! It's dangerous!

20:05.000 --> 20:05.400
Kang Wei!

20:05.400 --> 20:06.400
Get out first!

20:06.590 --> 20:07.920
Get out of the car first!

20:08.760 --> 20:09.480
Du Zhaohui,

20:09.510 --> 20:10.480
are you satisfied now?

20:10.480 --> 20:11.510
What are you talking about?

20:11.510 --> 20:12.030
Come on, let's go to the hospital!

20:12.030 --> 20:13.200
I need to save Kang Wei!

20:13.200 --> 20:13.920
You guys go ahead!

20:13.920 --> 20:15.300
Kang Wei! I need to save Kang Wei!

20:15.300 --> 20:16.390
I'll save Kang Wei!

20:17.480 --> 20:18.030
Let go of me!

20:18.030 --> 20:19.070
Come on! Let's go to the hospital!

20:19.070 --> 20:19.880
I need to save Kang Wei!

20:19.880 --> 20:20.640
Kang Wei!

20:20.640 --> 20:22.440
Let's go! To the hospital first!

20:23.480 --> 20:24.200
Come on!

20:25.830 --> 20:27.110
Wake up, man!

20:27.350 --> 20:28.110
Don't sleep!

20:28.110 --> 20:29.270
Don't fall asleep!

20:30.550 --> 20:31.640
Someone, help!

20:31.880 --> 20:33.410
Get him out of the car! Help!

20:37.310 --> 20:38.370
Be careful, nurse.

20:38.510 --> 20:40.840
Make sure she doesn't get any scars, okay?

20:44.880 --> 20:46.550
Xia Xiaolan, let's go to the ER.

20:46.550 --> 20:47.270
As for Mr. Kang,

20:47.270 --> 20:47.750
I will...

20:47.750 --> 20:48.410
Du Zhaohui,

20:49.000 --> 20:50.400
can you stay away from me?

20:50.720 --> 20:52.120
I'll say it one more time:

20:52.350 --> 20:53.720
if anything happens to Kang Wei,

20:53.720 --> 20:55.780
no amount of money will make up for it!

20:55.960 --> 20:57.030
I know that.

20:57.070 --> 20:57.790
As for Mr. Kang,

20:57.790 --> 20:58.880
I'll take full responsibility.

20:58.880 --> 21:00.340
And for you, I will also...

21:03.720 --> 21:05.270
First, you tried to
snatch our bidding documents,

21:05.270 --> 21:06.600
then you rammed into us—

21:06.830 --> 21:07.440
Du Zhaohui,

21:07.440 --> 21:09.440
is this how you "build" Shengcheng?

21:09.510 --> 21:11.200
It's just a guesthouse project.

21:11.200 --> 21:12.480
Did you really have to bring

21:12.480 --> 21:13.640
your family's tactics here?

21:13.640 --> 21:14.570
I'm telling you,

21:14.840 --> 21:15.830
this is Shengcheng!

21:15.830 --> 21:17.090
We follow the law here!

21:17.270 --> 21:17.960
It's all my fault.

21:17.960 --> 21:18.920
It's a misunderstanding!

21:18.920 --> 21:19.830
As for the guesthouse project,

21:19.830 --> 21:20.680
I already told Liu Tianquan

21:20.680 --> 21:21.680
to let you have it!

21:21.920 --> 21:23.720
I knew you were submitting the bid today.

21:23.720 --> 21:25.920
I just wanted to ask you out
for afternoon tea.

21:25.920 --> 21:26.920
I like you so much.

21:27.000 --> 21:28.400
How could I have hurt you?

21:30.160 --> 21:31.830
You darn scumbag!

21:32.150 --> 21:33.480
Driving like a maniac!

21:35.640 --> 21:36.680
How dare you kick my Young Master?

21:36.680 --> 21:37.510
Why did you hit my Young Master?

21:37.510 --> 21:39.440
One more word and I'll kick you too!

21:41.270 --> 21:42.200
Y-Young Master.

21:43.310 --> 21:44.110
Is that your tooth?

21:44.110 --> 21:44.790
My tooth!

21:46.030 --> 21:47.200
It really is your tooth!

21:47.200 --> 21:48.030
My tooth!

21:48.480 --> 21:49.340
I need a doctor.

21:49.440 --> 21:50.510
I need to be hospitalized!

21:50.510 --> 21:51.400
You barbarian!

21:52.440 --> 21:53.070
Doctor!

21:53.270 --> 21:53.960
Doctor! Doctor!

21:53.960 --> 21:54.790
Any doctor?

21:55.010 --> 21:55.960
Did I say you could leave?

21:55.960 --> 21:56.590
Zhenzhu.

21:56.680 --> 21:58.540
I'll beat you every time I see you!

21:58.640 --> 21:59.240
Calm down.

22:12.510 --> 22:13.680
The surgery went very well.

22:13.680 --> 22:14.270
He sustained

22:14.270 --> 22:15.600
a severe blow to the head

22:15.640 --> 22:16.770
and fractured ribs.

22:17.000 --> 22:18.160
He'll need time to recover.

22:18.160 --> 22:19.110
Once the anesthesia wears off,

22:19.110 --> 22:20.640
he could wake up at any time.

22:22.590 --> 22:23.650
Thank you, doctor.

22:28.030 --> 22:28.960
Are you alright?

22:38.110 --> 22:38.910
Young Master!

22:40.530 --> 22:41.610
Mr. Kang's surgery

22:41.640 --> 22:42.920
is finished.

22:43.440 --> 22:44.920
The doctor said it was a success.

22:44.920 --> 22:46.350
He should wake up in a few days.

22:46.350 --> 22:47.510
And as for Ms. Xia,

22:47.510 --> 22:48.440
she's been examined—

22:48.440 --> 22:49.310
only superficial wounds,

22:49.310 --> 22:50.270
no broken bones.

22:50.510 --> 22:51.000
Really?

22:52.590 --> 22:53.790
The woman I fancy

22:54.100 --> 22:55.650
sure is blessed with good fortune.

22:55.650 --> 22:57.060
Of course.

22:58.830 --> 23:00.400
What's all that fuss
over her bidding documents?

23:00.400 --> 23:02.110
Young Master, you guessed right.

23:02.110 --> 23:03.030
It was Liu Tianquan

23:03.030 --> 23:04.490
who got Ke Yixiong to do it.

23:04.720 --> 23:06.110
That bastard.

23:06.880 --> 23:08.340
I told him to throw the bid,

23:08.400 --> 23:10.480
and he actually dared to go against me.

23:10.480 --> 23:11.000
He's nothing but

23:11.000 --> 23:12.240
a lapdog to my father.

23:12.590 --> 23:14.640
If I hadn't taken a liking to his sister,

23:14.640 --> 23:16.040
he'd have been long gone.

23:16.510 --> 23:17.310
Call him here.

23:17.550 --> 23:18.720
I want to knock out

23:18.830 --> 23:20.880
all his teeth right in front of Ms. Xia!

23:20.880 --> 23:21.550
No problem.

23:22.040 --> 23:23.440
But that bastard said

23:23.510 --> 23:26.550
something urgent came up with the group
and ran off long ago!

23:26.550 --> 23:28.280
Young Master, have some water.

23:28.770 --> 23:30.000
Not the sharpest tool,

23:30.000 --> 23:31.060
but he sure can run.

23:31.310 --> 23:33.640
Does he think my old man
will cover for him?

23:33.720 --> 23:34.240
Fine.

23:34.480 --> 23:36.120
Add his teeth to his debt.

23:36.240 --> 23:36.880
Got it.

23:36.970 --> 23:37.830
I'll settle it with him when we get back.

23:37.830 --> 23:38.400
For sure.

23:40.270 --> 23:41.480
When a woman is injured,

23:41.480 --> 23:42.880
she's at her most vulnerable—

23:42.880 --> 23:44.200
most in need of someone to comfort her.

23:44.200 --> 23:45.070
Exactly.

23:45.720 --> 23:47.450
Has that Jerk Zhou shown up yet?

23:47.550 --> 23:47.960
Zhou?

23:49.880 --> 23:51.370
He's not here!

23:51.400 --> 23:52.730
He's still not here yet!

23:53.510 --> 23:54.510
He didn't rush here the moment he heard?

23:54.510 --> 23:55.070
Yeah.

23:56.440 --> 23:57.770
Are they having a fight?

23:57.790 --> 23:59.030
Must be, I think.

23:59.270 --> 23:59.830
Great.

24:01.000 --> 24:01.880
Flowers, fruit,

24:01.880 --> 24:02.830
and food from some restaurant—

24:02.830 --> 24:04.510
have it all sent to Ms. Xia's ward.

24:04.510 --> 24:05.510
Consider it done!

24:05.520 --> 24:06.250
Be thorough.

24:06.310 --> 24:07.440
Prepare a set for Mr. Kang too.

24:07.440 --> 24:07.880
Got it.

24:08.270 --> 24:09.530
I'll go arrange it now.

24:10.550 --> 24:12.280
Young Master is so thoughtful.

24:12.720 --> 24:14.120
Forgot to grab my jacket.

24:19.240 --> 24:19.750
Why did the client

24:19.750 --> 24:21.550
choose a place like this to meet?

24:36.550 --> 24:37.550
This should be it.

24:38.040 --> 24:38.830
I'll take a look over there.

24:38.830 --> 24:39.830
Okay, be careful.

24:43.830 --> 24:44.490
Zhou Cheng!

25:00.750 --> 25:01.310
Xiaolan?

25:01.890 --> 25:02.790
You look so pale.

25:02.790 --> 25:04.250
Let me get a doctor for you!

25:04.680 --> 25:05.210
I'm fine.

25:06.440 --> 25:06.960
No need.

25:07.720 --> 25:08.920
I just had a bad dream.

25:09.830 --> 25:11.000
Is Zhou Cheng here yet?

25:11.000 --> 25:11.640
Not yet.

25:11.640 --> 25:13.200
I've already paged him.

25:13.310 --> 25:14.030
The law firm said

25:14.030 --> 25:15.360
he went to meet a client.

25:15.510 --> 25:16.770
He should be here soon.

25:18.270 --> 25:19.720
How could this happen?

25:20.720 --> 25:21.780
No matter the cost,

25:21.880 --> 25:23.240
we have to make sure Kang Wei recovers!

25:23.240 --> 25:24.040
I understand.

25:24.270 --> 25:25.160
Kang Wei will be fine.

25:25.160 --> 25:25.820
Where is he?

25:27.160 --> 25:27.690
Xiaolan.

25:28.350 --> 25:29.010
How are you?

25:29.550 --> 25:30.110
I'm fine.

25:30.350 --> 25:31.350
How is Kang Wei?

25:33.040 --> 25:34.970
Kang Wei... he hasn't woken up yet.

25:35.680 --> 25:36.920
W-Who are you?

25:38.350 --> 25:39.330
I'm Xia Xiaolan.

25:39.880 --> 25:41.000
I was at the scene

25:41.110 --> 25:42.440
when the accident happened.

25:42.440 --> 25:43.300
You were there?

25:43.880 --> 25:45.140
Tell us what happened!

25:52.400 --> 25:53.350
Have you looked into

25:53.350 --> 25:54.240
that Kang fellow?

25:54.240 --> 25:55.400
Yes, Young Master.

25:55.750 --> 25:56.480
That Kang Wei

25:56.480 --> 25:58.080
is a friend of that Jerk Zhou.

25:58.200 --> 25:59.030
From the Jingcheng.

25:59.030 --> 26:00.270
He ran a stall at Renmin Bridge.

26:00.270 --> 26:01.680
His father was a soldier

26:01.960 --> 26:02.920
who died

26:02.920 --> 26:03.880
before he was born.

26:03.880 --> 26:05.920
Now his second uncle looks after him.

26:05.920 --> 26:07.640
His second uncle is Kang Lianming.

26:07.640 --> 26:09.550
That man is very mysterious, Young Master.

26:09.550 --> 26:10.750
I couldn't find any info on him.

26:10.750 --> 26:11.880
No idea what he does.

26:13.960 --> 26:15.760
Not an ordinary person, indeed.

26:17.550 --> 26:18.680
Xia Xiaolan was

26:18.920 --> 26:20.580
actually warning me earlier.

26:22.480 --> 26:24.310
She does care about me, after all.

26:24.310 --> 26:27.310
I was thinking—could it be

26:27.640 --> 26:29.500
that Ms. Xia was threatening you?

26:30.110 --> 26:31.240
You got a death wish?

26:36.830 --> 26:38.160
You did the right thing.

26:38.550 --> 26:39.200
That Gangdao businessman

26:39.200 --> 26:40.730
is staying here too, right?

26:41.200 --> 26:42.130
I want to see him.

26:42.750 --> 26:43.830
Yes, Du...

26:53.750 --> 26:54.510
Du Zhaohui.

26:55.200 --> 26:56.930
What are you trying to pull now?

26:57.880 --> 26:58.680
Xia Xiaolan,

26:59.480 --> 27:00.240
after getting kicked

27:00.240 --> 27:00.880
by your friend earlier,

27:00.880 --> 27:02.830
my head hasn't felt right.

27:03.160 --> 27:04.620
I get dizzy when I stand up.

27:04.960 --> 27:06.020
Excuse me for this.

27:07.010 --> 27:08.280
Could these two be

27:08.310 --> 27:09.750
Mr. Kang Wei's family?

27:11.000 --> 27:11.860
I'm Du Zhaohui.

27:15.240 --> 27:16.300
You're Du Zhaohui?

27:18.350 --> 27:20.210
What is Du Chengrong of Gangdao's

27:20.550 --> 27:21.880
Chengrong Group to you?

27:27.880 --> 27:29.680
He's my old... my daddy.

27:30.160 --> 27:31.890
Then Lin Lizhen is your mother.

27:32.550 --> 27:33.240
You also have

27:33.240 --> 27:34.550
a half-brother

27:35.110 --> 27:36.110
named Du Zhaoji,

27:36.200 --> 27:36.600
right?

27:37.360 --> 27:38.160
Young Master.

27:39.000 --> 27:40.030
Yes, Uncle.

27:41.070 --> 27:41.930
Let me tell you.

27:43.440 --> 27:44.570
This is Shengcheng.

27:44.830 --> 27:46.630
If you've done something wrong,

27:47.160 --> 27:48.850
you must take responsibility!

27:48.850 --> 27:49.880
I will, I will.

27:50.110 --> 27:51.240
Of course, I'll take responsibility.

27:51.240 --> 27:52.490
Medical bills, emotional distress—

27:52.490 --> 27:53.240
I'll cover everything.

27:53.240 --> 27:54.640
So what if you have money?

27:54.920 --> 27:56.920
You think money can fix everything?

27:57.040 --> 27:58.350
You've misunderstood.

27:58.350 --> 27:59.240
I hit someone,

27:59.400 --> 28:00.830
so I'll definitely take responsibility.

28:00.830 --> 28:01.590
Besides medical bills,

28:01.590 --> 28:02.480
if there's anything else you need,

28:02.480 --> 28:03.560
just tell me.

28:03.590 --> 28:05.590
If anything happens to Kang Wei,

28:05.880 --> 28:06.540
I guarantee

28:08.000 --> 28:11.000
your Du family won't be able to
bear the consequences!

28:11.720 --> 28:12.480
Wei is awake.

28:12.830 --> 28:13.510
I'll go get the doctor!

28:13.510 --> 28:13.920
Okay.

28:14.310 --> 28:15.040
Wei is awake.

28:16.010 --> 28:16.520
Wei!

28:16.550 --> 28:17.750
Let's get out of here.

28:22.000 --> 28:22.530
Xiaolan,

28:22.880 --> 28:23.880
let me take a look.

28:23.960 --> 28:26.560
Are you feeling uncomfortable
anywhere else?

28:27.070 --> 28:27.920
I'm fine.

28:38.350 --> 28:39.350
Does it hurt a lot?

28:44.790 --> 28:45.350
Wei.

28:45.370 --> 28:46.040
Mom.

28:47.350 --> 28:48.310
Where am I?

28:48.880 --> 28:50.080
This is the hospital.

28:51.110 --> 28:52.590
The patient's condition is stable.

28:52.590 --> 28:53.830
He'll need time to recover.

28:53.830 --> 28:54.790
But for the next couple of days,

28:54.790 --> 28:56.250
avoid anything too solid—

28:56.270 --> 28:57.590
stick mainly to a liquid diet.

28:57.590 --> 28:58.240
Okay.

29:01.030 --> 29:01.960
Second Uncle,

29:02.200 --> 29:03.480
why are you here too?

29:03.790 --> 29:04.680
Something this serious happened to you.

29:04.680 --> 29:05.810
How could I not come?

29:06.110 --> 29:07.310
If you feel unwell anywhere,

29:07.310 --> 29:08.010
tell me.

29:08.960 --> 29:10.890
For now, just focus on recovering.

29:12.480 --> 29:13.160
Sis Bai,

29:13.880 --> 29:14.880
where is Xiaolan?

29:15.440 --> 29:16.230
She's fine.

29:17.240 --> 29:18.400
Stop talking now.

29:18.750 --> 29:20.030
Close your eyes

29:20.310 --> 29:21.310
and get some rest.

29:23.680 --> 29:24.480
My poor child.

29:29.110 --> 29:29.880
Xia Xiaolan,

29:30.440 --> 29:31.700
this is all your fault!

29:32.470 --> 29:33.960
If you hadn't wanted to
come to Shengcheng,

29:33.960 --> 29:35.880
Cheng and Wei wouldn't have come here.

29:35.880 --> 29:37.550
If you hadn't insisted on doing business,

29:37.550 --> 29:39.310
Wei wouldn't have gotten into an accident!

29:39.310 --> 29:39.880
Auntie,

29:40.360 --> 29:41.070
I understand you're saying this

29:41.070 --> 29:42.270
because you're worried about Wei.

29:42.270 --> 29:42.790
But what happened to Wei

29:42.790 --> 29:44.880
really has nothing to do with Xiaolan!

29:44.880 --> 29:46.270
Wei is already

29:46.270 --> 29:47.400
an adult who can make

29:47.400 --> 29:48.460
his own decisions.

29:48.560 --> 29:49.070
Cheng...

29:49.070 --> 29:49.720
Auntie.

29:50.270 --> 29:52.610
The business we're doing
is completely legitimate.

29:52.610 --> 29:53.940
Kang Wei's car accident

29:53.960 --> 29:55.490
has nothing to do with that.

29:56.160 --> 29:56.960
If you don't want him

29:56.960 --> 29:58.480
staying in Shengcheng anymore,

29:58.480 --> 29:59.510
you can wait until he wakes up

29:59.510 --> 30:01.110
and discuss it with him then.

30:01.350 --> 30:02.790
Arguing here right now

30:03.070 --> 30:04.350
won't help him at all.

30:04.790 --> 30:05.190
You...

30:05.270 --> 30:05.790
Yun.

30:07.200 --> 30:07.930
I don't care.

30:08.410 --> 30:09.590
I'm going to arrange a transfer

30:09.590 --> 30:10.590
for Wei right now.

30:11.110 --> 30:11.720
Auntie,

30:12.960 --> 30:15.270
if you transfer him back to Jingcheng,

30:15.550 --> 30:16.920
it'll be a long trip—

30:16.920 --> 30:18.000
car and plane.

30:18.350 --> 30:19.510
He just had surgery.

30:19.510 --> 30:20.880
His body can't take it.

30:21.830 --> 30:23.360
Why don't you wait a few days

30:23.640 --> 30:26.240
until he recovers a bit
before taking him back?

30:26.440 --> 30:28.040
Wei is a very stubborn child.

30:28.590 --> 30:30.030
If he recovers,

30:30.240 --> 30:31.700
he won't come back with me.

30:31.720 --> 30:32.240
Yun,

30:32.750 --> 30:33.350
I think...

30:33.960 --> 30:35.360
the girl has a point.

30:38.520 --> 30:39.040
Auntie,

30:39.440 --> 30:40.170
don't worry.

30:40.690 --> 30:42.160
Since I'm the one
who talked you out of it,

30:42.160 --> 30:44.260
I'll take responsibility for the outcome.

30:44.260 --> 30:45.330
When he recovers,

30:45.350 --> 30:46.880
if he refuses to go with you,

30:46.880 --> 30:48.740
I'll kick him out the door myself!

30:48.900 --> 30:50.430
Du Zhaohui you saw just now—

30:50.550 --> 30:52.610
I was the one who kicked him like that.

30:56.200 --> 30:57.400
You girl...

30:57.830 --> 30:59.030
What's your name?

30:59.720 --> 31:00.450
Bai Zhenzhu.

31:00.790 --> 31:02.960
I used to run a stall at Renmin Bridge.

31:03.400 --> 31:04.350
Now I've opened

31:04.350 --> 31:06.350
a building materials shop of my own.

31:09.350 --> 31:10.150
Alright then.

31:10.640 --> 31:12.750
I'll listen to you.

31:13.550 --> 31:15.210
We won't transfer him for now.

31:15.640 --> 31:16.230
Okay.

31:17.070 --> 31:17.730
Zhou Cheng,

31:17.760 --> 31:18.920
take Xiaolan back to her ward.

31:18.920 --> 31:20.650
I'm going to get some hot water.

31:22.070 --> 31:22.750
Miss Bai!

31:23.510 --> 31:24.480
I'll go with you.

31:24.510 --> 31:24.880
Okay.

31:27.590 --> 31:28.390
Second Uncle,

31:28.840 --> 31:30.000
then I'll take her...

31:30.000 --> 31:30.330
Okay.

31:30.480 --> 31:31.550
I'll go help them.

31:31.550 --> 31:31.930
Okay.

31:33.240 --> 31:33.790
Let's go.

31:35.750 --> 31:36.280
Careful.

31:39.780 --> 31:40.300
Come on.

31:45.200 --> 31:45.680
Come on.

31:48.200 --> 31:49.600
Visiting hours are over.

31:52.160 --> 31:53.360
Can I stay overnight?

31:53.400 --> 31:54.160
Family members only.

31:54.160 --> 31:55.240
Are you her family?

31:57.440 --> 31:58.680
I... sort of am.

31:59.270 --> 32:00.000
"Sort of?"

32:00.240 --> 32:01.370
So you're not, then.

32:01.400 --> 32:02.530
Come back tomorrow.

32:04.310 --> 32:04.960
It's okay.

32:05.440 --> 32:06.550
Go back and rest.

32:06.640 --> 32:08.040
You've had a long day too.

32:08.480 --> 32:09.350
I'll be fine.

32:09.960 --> 32:11.240
If you don't leave now,

32:11.920 --> 32:13.590
the nurse might call the police

32:13.590 --> 32:15.320
to report you for harassing me.

32:17.440 --> 32:18.570
Alright, I'm going.

32:23.440 --> 32:25.440
I'll bring you breakfast tomorrow.

32:25.870 --> 32:26.830
Please leave now, sir.

32:26.830 --> 32:27.750
The patient needs rest.

32:27.750 --> 32:28.750
Okay. Rest well.

32:37.370 --> 32:38.000
Sis Bai,

32:39.160 --> 32:40.640
thank you so much for today.

32:40.640 --> 32:41.270
You don't have to

32:41.270 --> 32:42.750
be so polite with me.

32:44.510 --> 32:45.570
I've been thinking

32:45.790 --> 32:47.830
that Xiaolan hasn't been
doing well lately.

32:47.830 --> 32:49.000
Should we ask her mom

32:49.000 --> 32:50.510
to come and keep her company?

32:50.510 --> 32:52.310
Xiaolan asked me not to tell her mom.

32:52.310 --> 32:53.440
She even specifically
called her mom earlier

32:53.440 --> 32:55.480
and said she'd gone to Longcheng recently.

32:55.480 --> 32:57.340
She doesn't want her mom to worry.

32:57.510 --> 32:58.880
Since she doesn't want us to tell,

32:58.880 --> 33:00.110
let's not say anything.

33:00.110 --> 33:01.710
I'll come by early tomorrow.

33:04.640 --> 33:05.310
Second Uncle,

33:05.310 --> 33:06.510
l-let me walk you out.

33:06.880 --> 33:07.340
No need.

33:07.350 --> 33:08.160
I can manage on my own.

33:08.160 --> 33:09.110
It's fine, really. I'll walk you.

33:09.110 --> 33:10.070
Let's go together then.

33:10.070 --> 33:10.600
Let's go.

33:14.750 --> 33:17.070
In this era, there aren't that many cars

33:17.070 --> 33:18.790
on the streets of Shengcheng yet.

33:18.790 --> 33:20.070
A serious car accident

33:20.070 --> 33:21.440
is a rare occurrence.

33:22.240 --> 33:23.440
Du Zhaohui's panic

33:23.440 --> 33:24.840
didn't seem fake either.

33:26.550 --> 33:27.480
If it really was

33:27.480 --> 33:28.880
just an accident...

33:36.590 --> 33:38.050
Why is it a car crash again?

33:38.880 --> 33:40.880
Why that same piercing sound again?

33:41.680 --> 33:42.410
Could this be

33:43.110 --> 33:44.750
fate warning me?

33:52.030 --> 33:52.790
Zhou Cheng?

33:53.720 --> 33:54.920
Why did you come back?

33:57.750 --> 33:58.680
I didn't want to leave you alone

33:58.680 --> 33:59.160
here.

34:04.000 --> 34:04.590
Young Master,

34:04.590 --> 34:05.720
if you go back to Gangdao now,

34:05.720 --> 34:07.310
won't you just hand Ms. Xia over

34:07.310 --> 34:07.880
to that Jerk Zhou?

34:07.880 --> 34:09.440
Could you be any more stupid?

34:09.440 --> 34:10.190
With Zhou here,

34:10.190 --> 34:11.449
I don't stand a chance.

34:12.840 --> 34:13.760
What, should I stick around

34:13.760 --> 34:14.690
and get beaten up by that Kang—

34:14.690 --> 34:15.889
whatever his name is?

34:16.070 --> 34:17.870
But he was right about one thing.

34:18.630 --> 34:20.360
My old man doesn't only have me.

34:20.590 --> 34:22.670
People in Gangdao are eyeing us hungrily.

34:22.670 --> 34:23.670
They might take this opportunity

34:23.670 --> 34:24.710
to stab me in the back.

34:24.710 --> 34:26.170
I should go back and check.

34:26.230 --> 34:27.150
Then what about Shengcheng?

34:27.150 --> 34:27.760
Do we need to find someone...

34:27.760 --> 34:28.820
Don't do anything.

34:29.550 --> 34:31.550
That Kang guy is no ordinary person.

34:32.150 --> 34:33.630
Just do whatever the traffic police say.

34:33.630 --> 34:34.630
First thing tomorrow morning,

34:34.630 --> 34:35.880
have a lawyer come to the hospital.

34:35.880 --> 34:36.960
Whatever they ask,

34:37.380 --> 34:38.679
we'll agree—as long as it's legal.

34:38.679 --> 34:39.010
Okay.

34:39.190 --> 34:39.840
Got it.

34:42.920 --> 34:44.380
I just went to check on Wei.

34:45.030 --> 34:47.070
Second Uncle was really angry today.

34:47.070 --> 34:49.000
If Wei's surgery hadn't gone well,

34:50.510 --> 34:51.320
I'm afraid...

34:51.980 --> 34:53.420
Kang Wei always said

34:53.480 --> 34:55.150
Second Uncle never paid him
much attention.

34:55.150 --> 34:57.010
Seems that wasn't entirely true.

35:02.160 --> 35:02.920
So, do you think

35:02.920 --> 35:04.520
Du Zhaohui did it on purpose?

35:05.550 --> 35:06.350
Probably not.

35:07.710 --> 35:08.710
He has no motive.

35:09.590 --> 35:10.550
And he wouldn't be stupid enough

35:10.550 --> 35:12.350
to commit a crime in Shengcheng.

35:14.840 --> 35:16.170
I know he still likes you

35:17.000 --> 35:18.330
and wants to pursue you.

35:19.190 --> 35:20.390
You're so wonderful.

35:20.880 --> 35:22.940
It's only natural for men to like you.

35:23.320 --> 35:24.000
However,

35:24.510 --> 35:26.230
I'll keep working hard to improve.

35:26.230 --> 35:27.760
I won't give him an opening.

35:34.030 --> 35:34.820
Well, that depends on

35:34.820 --> 35:36.880
whether you're competitive enough.

35:42.140 --> 35:45.860
♪ I don't know when it started ♪

35:45.000 --> 35:45.880
Why are you staring at me?

35:45.880 --> 35:49.160
♪ But my world suddenly became bright ♪

35:48.150 --> 35:49.290
You're covered in injuries…

35:49.290 --> 35:52.970
♪ In the second our eyes met ♪

35:51.150 --> 35:51.920
It must hurt.

35:54.110 --> 35:56.160
♪ I knew it had to be you ♪

35:56.230 --> 35:56.820
Don't move.

35:56.820 --> 36:00.390
♪ Fireworks paint the sky tonight ♪

36:00.580 --> 36:03.480
♪ Yet you'd rather stand in the rain ♪

36:01.110 --> 36:03.150
It doesn't matter
that you have injuries on your face.

36:03.150 --> 36:04.150
You're still beautiful.

36:03.760 --> 36:07.480
♪ Every secret you keep inside ♪

36:05.670 --> 36:08.200
You really know
how to make a girl feel better.

36:09.220 --> 36:10.480
♪ I gather slowly, one by one ♪

36:09.440 --> 36:10.510
What about your hand?

36:10.510 --> 36:16.400
♪ Countless times,
I've tried to tell you ♪

36:10.920 --> 36:12.780
Did the doctor check it properly?

36:13.590 --> 36:14.440
Don't worry.

36:14.550 --> 36:15.880
They did a full check-up.

36:15.880 --> 36:16.510
I'm fine.

36:17.150 --> 36:17.800
Let me see.

36:17.360 --> 36:19.480
♪ Even if the world turned upside down ♪

36:19.150 --> 36:20.000
You're not feeling any discomfort, right?

36:19.510 --> 36:21.190
♪ I'd always find you ♪

36:21.570 --> 36:24.540
♪ My beloved ♪

36:23.670 --> 36:24.470
Zhou Cheng...

36:25.880 --> 36:26.540
Don't move.

36:26.620 --> 36:30.480
♪ I'd give anything just to see you ♪

36:28.400 --> 36:30.200
I just want to hold you like this.

36:30.790 --> 36:34.570
♪ I'd move heaven and earth for you ♪

36:34.590 --> 36:38.010
♪ I trust that time will lead me to you ♪

36:38.040 --> 36:40.040
♪ I can forget everything ♪

36:38.760 --> 36:39.320
Xiaolan.

36:40.060 --> 36:42.060
♪ Except your eyes ♪

36:42.080 --> 36:45.790
♪ I see the moments we shared ♪

36:42.110 --> 36:43.000
I was so scared.

36:45.360 --> 36:46.070
I want to...

36:45.810 --> 36:49.190
♪ I hear you calling out our vows ♪

36:47.760 --> 36:48.820
hold you like this,

36:49.210 --> 36:53.100
♪ I believe, and I hope you do too ♪

36:50.000 --> 36:51.330
for as long as possible,

36:52.230 --> 36:53.120
and never leave your side.

36:53.120 --> 36:54.540
♪ Whenever I see you ♪

36:54.570 --> 36:57.950
♪ Our love echoes ♪

37:12.630 --> 37:13.960
Granny Yu, you're back.

37:14.670 --> 37:15.400
Um...

37:16.200 --> 37:17.440
I made some turnip cake.

37:17.440 --> 37:19.700
Could you try it
and see if I made it right?

37:22.110 --> 37:23.800
Why isn't Xiaolan up yet?

37:24.070 --> 37:25.200
I'll go check on her.

37:27.190 --> 37:27.960
Didn't she

37:27.960 --> 37:29.230
call yesterday and say

37:29.490 --> 37:31.110
she was going to Longcheng for a few days

37:31.110 --> 37:32.840
to discuss the clothing store?

37:33.280 --> 37:34.680
Your memory is terrible.

37:34.840 --> 37:37.170
How will you
manage the shop for her later?

37:39.440 --> 37:40.840
There's no hope for you.

37:41.510 --> 37:43.150
I... I just forgot.

37:43.280 --> 37:45.880
She rarely goes on business trips
so suddenly.

37:47.230 --> 37:49.430
Why did she go to Longcheng so suddenly?

37:49.640 --> 37:51.440
And stay there for several days?

37:59.400 --> 38:00.150
Alright.

38:00.360 --> 38:01.290
Go back quickly.

38:01.440 --> 38:02.710
If the nurse catches you,

38:02.710 --> 38:04.570
they won't let you visit anymore.

38:31.110 --> 38:31.920
Don't worry.

38:32.470 --> 38:33.400
It doesn't hurt.

38:38.920 --> 38:40.070
I'll head off then.

38:40.760 --> 38:41.280
Okay.

38:43.190 --> 38:44.070
I, uh...

38:44.550 --> 38:46.360
have to go to the court this morning.

38:46.360 --> 38:47.440
In the afternoon... uh...

38:47.440 --> 38:48.670
I'll come over early if I can.

38:48.670 --> 38:50.000
Take care of yourself.

38:50.440 --> 38:52.370
Call Zhenzhu if you need anything.

38:53.360 --> 38:54.150
Be careful.

38:56.670 --> 38:57.200
I'm fine.

39:02.480 --> 39:03.230
About Wei's mom,

39:03.230 --> 39:04.630
you don't need to worry too much either.

39:04.630 --> 39:05.550
She was just

39:05.550 --> 39:06.190
too anxious yesterday;

39:06.190 --> 39:08.050
that's why she said those things.

39:09.280 --> 39:09.760
Okay.

39:09.960 --> 39:10.690
Hurry and go.

39:11.480 --> 39:12.110
I'm off.

39:14.320 --> 39:15.250
Time for rounds!

39:18.290 --> 39:19.350
Get down, get down.

39:19.670 --> 39:20.070
Quick.

39:23.880 --> 39:25.410
Alright, the nurse is gone.

39:26.710 --> 39:28.510
Comrade Zhou Cheng, be careful.

39:31.320 --> 39:32.180
Then I'm going.

39:34.110 --> 39:35.640
I'm really going this time.

39:37.320 --> 39:37.850
Bye-bye.

39:40.960 --> 39:41.490
Bye-bye.

39:49.920 --> 39:51.710
Am I overthinking?

39:52.550 --> 39:53.550
Zhou Cheng...

39:54.280 --> 39:56.340
seems somehow different from usual.

40:04.110 --> 40:05.360
I've been coming to the hospital
more often lately,

40:05.360 --> 40:07.550
picking up medicine for my mom
or taking her to get injections.

40:07.550 --> 40:09.110
You're such a filial child.

40:09.320 --> 40:10.720
And so kind-hearted too.

40:11.320 --> 40:12.250
This is the ward.

40:12.850 --> 40:13.180
Okay.

40:13.190 --> 40:14.650
Here, give me the thermos.

40:19.280 --> 40:21.030
Here, give me the fruit as well.

40:21.360 --> 40:21.760
Let me.

40:21.840 --> 40:22.550
Thank you.

40:22.590 --> 40:23.510
No problem, Auntie.

40:23.510 --> 40:24.150
I'll be going now.

40:24.150 --> 40:24.480
Okay, okay.

40:24.480 --> 40:25.190
Goodbye, Auntie.

40:25.190 --> 40:25.720
Goodbye.

40:27.540 --> 40:28.490
Morning, Auntie.

40:28.490 --> 40:29.550
Morning, Miss Bai!

40:29.630 --> 40:30.800
Who was that girl?

40:31.620 --> 40:32.550
I went to get food

40:32.550 --> 40:34.110
but couldn't find the place.

40:34.110 --> 40:35.510
That child took me there

40:35.510 --> 40:36.800
and brought me back.

40:37.290 --> 40:38.190
I bought some fruit,

40:38.190 --> 40:39.280
and she insisted on carrying it for me.

40:39.280 --> 40:40.550
She's such a kind girl.

40:43.760 --> 40:44.760
Why have you...

40:45.630 --> 40:47.000
come so early today?

40:48.230 --> 40:50.070
I came to bring breakfast
for the two of them.

40:50.070 --> 40:51.730
The hospital food isn't good.

40:52.030 --> 40:53.070
Auntie, since you're here,

40:53.070 --> 40:55.070
I'll go bring breakfast to Xiaolan.

40:55.280 --> 40:56.540
Don't be in such a rush.

40:56.590 --> 40:58.120
Let's eat together in a bit!

40:58.320 --> 40:58.780
Well...

40:58.900 --> 41:00.630
A-Are you done cleaning him up?

41:01.070 --> 41:01.710
Mom,

41:01.800 --> 41:03.200
you don't need to wipe me,

41:03.280 --> 41:05.110
or you'll rub my skin off.

41:06.630 --> 41:07.800
What do you know?

41:16.000 --> 41:16.460
Senior.

41:17.840 --> 41:19.040
I've thought it over.

41:20.480 --> 41:22.410
That didn't look like an accident.

41:22.590 --> 41:24.480
How could it be such a coincidence?

41:24.480 --> 41:25.920
Shi Kai and I just got a lead

41:25.920 --> 41:26.510
and were about to investigate

41:26.510 --> 41:28.640
-the key information...
-Zhou Cheng!

41:31.070 --> 41:31.730
Zhou Cheng.

41:32.880 --> 41:34.320
Come with me to Shi Kai's hometown

41:34.320 --> 41:35.480
in a couple of days.

41:37.230 --> 41:39.280
His wife, child, and mother

41:40.160 --> 41:41.490
are all waiting for him.

41:47.360 --> 41:48.670
This is...

41:49.280 --> 41:51.140
some compensation from the firm.

41:52.800 --> 41:53.760
As for the case,

41:54.230 --> 41:55.360
let's put it on hold.

41:55.760 --> 41:56.440
Wait for the results from the police

41:56.440 --> 41:57.510
and the court.

41:58.440 --> 41:59.840
When we get back from Shi Kai's hometown,

41:59.840 --> 42:01.370
you should take a break too.

42:01.630 --> 42:03.230
You've been busy for so long.

42:03.920 --> 42:05.670
Spend some time with your girlfriend.

42:05.670 --> 42:06.110
Right?

42:07.030 --> 42:08.090
Work is important,

42:08.920 --> 42:10.320
but family matters more.

43:20.280 --> 43:22.190
Not bad,

43:22.480 --> 43:23.590
the hospital bed.

43:26.030 --> 43:27.230
When did you get here?

43:27.970 --> 43:29.630
I've been here for a while now,

43:31.000 --> 43:33.200
but you've been staring off into space.

43:33.230 --> 43:34.030
You haven't been yourself

43:34.030 --> 43:35.110
since yesterday.

43:35.670 --> 43:36.190
What's wrong?
